{"tid":2112042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大陸又贏美國! 大陸戲院重開, 美國戲院重開無期.","createTime":"2020-07-17T04:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T11:44:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e64de21677e454101db5c00b4b01a04ff5581ce4","tid":2112042,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"大陞戲院重開. 美國戲院重開無期. &nbsp; (香港戲院都係)<br />\n大陸靠病毒取代荷里活? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>中國國家電影局也於今天公佈，低風險地區的戲院可於七月二十日起重開。目前中國大陸對武漢肺炎的疫情依然不同城市和地區，劃分成低、中、高風險三個類別，而是次重開的只在低風險地區的戲院，中風險和高風險地區的戲院仍然停業。<br />\n<br />\n即使戲院重開，但是在不少安排上也需採取防疫措施。當中觀眾及員工均需要量度體溫，溫度高於攝氏37.3度不得入場。而售票方面，全部戲院採用網上實名購票，而觀眾間的距離需要至少在一米或以上，而每場的入座率最高也只有三成。而觀眾入場需要全程佩戴口罩，影廳內不得飲食之餘，就連戲院也不售賣飲食。 另一方面，即使戲院重開，排出的場次也只能是平時的一半，而且要控制觀影時間，每場不能超過兩小時。至於不同影廳，也要安排不同時間入場，以分散觀眾。</em><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/76180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F76180&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=9edf5fcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/76180</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>武漢肺炎令全球戲院關閉，最近加州戲院於短暫重開後又再次宣佈關閉<strong>，有電影業專家悲觀估計，戲院可能要到下年年中才有重開機會</strong>，亦即是本年度至出年初所有大片，都要延遲上映。<br />\n媒體分析師Doug Creutz表示：「我們可以預計，本土戲院將會關閉到2021年中，我不覺得各大電影公司，會有興趣將其大製作電影在限制了人數的戲院上映。</em>」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200717/A5A2ESSFZUZDQIX6CBBYACJR4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200717%2FA5A2ESSFZUZDQIX6CBBYACJR4Q%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=278582dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200717%2FA5A2ESSFZUZDQIX6CBBYACJR4Q%2F&h=636c4f09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200717/A5A2ESSFZUZDQIX6CBBYACJR4Q/</a>"},{"pid":"320a8dc729f93db61110dcca1fcc3e69a5ca6305","tid":2112042,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:24:47.000Z","msg":"老共可能盤算: 借病毒取代美國, 成世界第一強國. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1d68bfefdc96445152245f7526f5f62179f62a","tid":2112042,"uid":22694,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"大陸一上<br />\n美國個個屋企有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6327f36dbe4f4724aa049b5e72ecc4709cf677a3","tid":2112042,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e1d68bfefdc96445152245f7526f5f62179f62a","tid":2112042,"uid":22694,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"大陸一上<br />\n美國個個屋企有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"戲院先係電影業成功既指標, 甚至係演藝界成功既指標<br />\n<br />\n星馬網絡娛樂都好賺錢, 有無人話星馬演藝界好威?"},{"pid":"19b954748d81e45b0f5b51b3d7b85d93fc421d6d","tid":2112042,"uid":81052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"又重開<br />\n之前開左幾耐?<br />\n<br />\n唔係一早就話零確診咩，點解咁耐先開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389af3068db47fd8f1ae5c62ed84690641f1147e","tid":2112042,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19b954748d81e45b0f5b51b3d7b85d93fc421d6d","tid":2112042,"uid":81052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"又重開<br />\n之前開左幾耐?<br />\n<br />\n唔係一早就話零確診咩，點解咁耐先開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025b03cc8d3ea459d1021be8072b929ea845651f","tid":2112042,"uid":174601,"like":2,